ot convert to string in frontend class</li>\n<li>Fixed: Problem with cirillic charachter</li>\n<li>Fixed: Wrong count in filter widgets</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.0.4 &#8211; Released: Jul 8, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Filters show all attributes in shop and product taxonomy pages</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.0.3 &#8211; Released: Jul 6, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Wrong query object in layered nav query with WooCommerce 2.6.2</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.0.2 &#8211; Released: Jul 4, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Filters disappears in sort count select on Avada theme</li>\n<li>Fixed: Filter by attributes doesn&#8217;t works with WooCommerce 2.5</li>\n<li>Fixed: rtrim waring in untrailingslashit</li>\n<li>Fixed: Wrong filter on category page with WooCommerce 2.6.2</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.0.1 &#8211; Released: Jun 14, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: print empty li tag after update to version 3.0.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.0.0 &#8211; Released: Jun 13, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Support to WooCommece 2.6</li>\n<li>Tweak: Layered navigation management</li>\n<li>Tweak: English Typo</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.2 &#8211; Released: May 16, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Wrong reset button link in product category page</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.1 &#8211; Released: May 04, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: $class variable are not defined</li>\n<li>Fixed: Filter by list-attribute doesn&#8217;t works in versio 2.9.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.0 &#8211; Released: May 02, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Filtering issue with YITH WooCommerce Brands Add-on Premium</li>\n<li>Fixed: HTML5 Validation (attribute name not allowed in ul element)</li>\n<li>Fixed: z-index not set to -1 when user close dropdown filters with click in page area</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.8.1 &#8211; Released: Mar 10, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Dropdown issue with Remy Theme</li>\n<li>Fixed: $.fn.slider is not a function after click on reset filter</li>\n<li>Fixed: Reset filter in product category page doesn&#8217;t works</li>\n<li>Fixed: Plugin panel option style issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.