>\n</p>\n\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:979:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625678\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625678\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;This is the mail settings page for the plugin, you can find it inside the YIT Plugins menu item. You can configure the mail with the review reminder.&lt;/p&gt;\"></a><p><p>This is the mail settings page for the plugin, you can find it inside the YIT Plugins menu item. You can configure the mail with the review reminder.</p></p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625678\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625678\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;This is the blocklist page for the plugin. You can add or remove users from the blocklist.&lt;/p&gt;\"></a><p><p>This is the blocklist page for the plugin. You can add or remove users from the blocklist.</p></p></li></ol>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:84:\"Allows you to send a reminder to customers with an invitation to do a review&hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder.1.4.0.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:2:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:85:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625678\";s:7:\"caption\";s:156:\"<p>This is the mail settings page for the plugin, you can find it inside the YIT Plugins menu item. You can configure the mail with the review reminder.</p>\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:85:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625678\";s:7:\"caption\";s:97:\"<p>This is the blocklist page for the plugin. You can add or remove users from the blocklist.</p>\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:8:\"products\";s:8:\"products\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:6:\"themes\";s:6:\"themes\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:3: