rg/yithemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.9.6\";s:12:\"requires_php\";b:0;s:6:\"rating\";d:58;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:7;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:1;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:8;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:16;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:1;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:1000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:17816;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2018-05-16 2:20pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-04-07\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:65:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:1945:\"<p>What do you do when you have no more stock of one of your products and your customers want to buy it? You risk to lose them, unless you make a system available for them to be notified of the product coming back to stock. Then, why not using a plugin that allows them to be added to a waiting list and being informed in an automatic and efficient way? This is what YITH WooCommerce Waiting List does, allowing you to loyalise them in a simple way and at the same time not lose them.</p>\n<p><strong>Main features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A form to receive a reminding email when the item is back in stock</li>\n<li>&#8220;Add me to the waiting list&#8221; button for logged users</li>\n<li>Summary metabox with the number of waiting user and a rapid way to contact them</li>\n<li>Customization of the &#8220;Notify me&#8221; button</li>\n<li>Email basic template to notify users for an item back in stock</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Gợi ý</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Waiting List, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Waiting List.</p>\n<h3>Phiên dịch</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tiếng Anh</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you can&#8217;t find this plugin in your language and want to translate it, use the dedicated tool at <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/it/default/wp-plugins/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list\" title=\"Translating WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Translating WordPress</a>.<br />\nOr, if you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send it as an email attachment from our <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/contact/\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">Contacts page</a> and we will bundle into YITH WooCommerce Waiting List.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:241:\"<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Waiting List</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:3085:\"<h4>1.3.0</h4>\n<p>Released May 16 &#8211; 2018</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.4.0 RC1.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.9.6 RC2.</li>\n<li>New: General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) compliance.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Update: Language files.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.0</h4>\n<p>Released Feb 02 &#8211; 2018</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.3.0.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.9.2</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Fix: Product name including variations on plugin&#8217;s emails.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2</h4>\n<p>Released Oct 12 &#8211; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.2.0.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.8.2</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1</h4>\n<p>Released Apr 21 &#8211; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.0.4.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Fix: Prevent duplicated post meta for product.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0</h4>\n<p>Released Mar 29 &#8211; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.0.0 RC2.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.7.3.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.8</h4>\n<p>Released