>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:287:\"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Waiting List</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:823:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625824\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625824\" alt=\"The plugin admin page.\"></a><p>The plugin admin page.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625824\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625824\" alt=\"Plugin frontend for logged in user\"></a><p>Plugin frontend for logged in user</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1625824\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1625824\" alt=\"Plugin frontend for guest user\"></a><p>Plugin frontend for guest user</p></li></ol>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:112:\"This plugin enables registered users to request an email notification when an out-of-stock product comes&hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list.1.3.0.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:82:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625824\";s:7:\"caption\";s:22:\"The plugin admin page.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:82:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625824\";s:7:\"caption\";s:34:\"Plugin frontend for logged in user\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:82:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1625824\";s:7:\"caption\";s:30:\"Plugin f